{"tid":1269523,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"繼<淪落人>後，港產片<作家的謊言>獲邀做芝加哥影展閉幕片","createTime":"2019-06-30T15:00:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T11:19:51.000Z","uid":119778,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"127fb2911afd1c694d3d9b07c69bd9f07bcde90f","tid":1269523,"uid":119778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:00:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190629/_2019062922015721193.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190629%2F_2019062922015721193.jpg&h=a2fcbb71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由張建聲監製兼主演電影《作家的謊言：筆忠誘罪》，近日獲邀成為美國芝加哥「亞洲躍動電影展」( ASIAN POP-UP CINEMA ) 第九季閉幕電影，張建聲及導演兼監製孫立基，會在10月一同赴美出席影展。<br />\n<br />\n該影展於上一季揀選黃秋生主演的《淪落人》播映，今次《作家》能成為閉幕片，令團隊甚為鼓舞。張建聲說：「係受寵若驚，呢個電影節喺 Facebook 聯絡我，我嘅戲係從來未曾參加過外國影展，所以當收到呢個訊息時，我有啲懷疑，就搵咗公司同事了解，原來真喎。多謝自己嘅團隊好大付出，所有嘢都係感恩。」<br />\n<br />\n《作家》是百分百的本土製作，能打着港產旗號走向國際，張建聲坦言：「喺呢個時候呢個環境下，一切都得來不易，好似我一有時間就去謝票一樣，我相信試咗可能唔得，唔試就一定唔得，希望將我哋港產片繼續發揚光大甚至乎衝出亞洲去到美國咁遠。呢套戲係我3年嘅心血，亦係我哋上上下下團隊結晶品，希望票房令投資方滿意嘅話開續集。」"},{"pid":"5cc1f4cb4c93fa3a3d9dbdcf8ca6fc4c7b7e569d","tid":1269523,"uid":16743,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:34:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b77aaa9a21398046b383d9f99ea1b3d0d4ad08ae","tid":1269523,"uid":85774,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:38:23.000Z","msg":"俾左幾多錢大會？"},{"pid":"2ad1a8afb19899459ced9ddb0b4dfa87c33e70ea","tid":1269523,"uid":38705,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:40:43.000Z","msg":"呢套野有驚喜<br />\n支持港產片"},{"pid":"18e8d65047d04157419ee47737036c69d940c59e","tid":1269523,"uid":16743,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b77aaa9a21398046b383d9f99ea1b3d0d4ad08ae","tid":1269523,"uid":85774,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:38:23.000Z","msg":"俾左幾多錢大會？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:50:29.000Z","msg":"姓燒嘅比唔比得起呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"845b5e6008a479f3e4a24cd4eb7a9c94670d92bb","tid":1269523,"uid":109318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18e8d65047d04157419ee47737036c69d940c59e","tid":1269523,"uid":16743,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b77aaa9a21398046b383d9f99ea1b3d0d4ad08ae","tid":1269523,"uid":85774,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:38:23.000Z","msg":"俾左幾多錢大會？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:50:29.000Z","msg":"姓燒嘅比唔比得起呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T18:27:41.000Z","msg":"知唔知有好多濕9電影展<br />\n以前聽藝人講過<br />\n你比得起少少錢 就可以係美國 歐洲求其有個電影展<br />\n甚至拎獎都得<br />\n（唔知lee個電影展有無水分）"},{"pid":"fabe06f9f39ea960b71a22513ffab5b72742f7aa","tid":1269523,"uid":119778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"845b5e6008a479f3e4a24cd4eb7a9c94670d92bb","tid":1269523,"uid":109318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18e8d65047d04157419ee47737036c69d940c59e","tid":1269523,"uid":16743,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b77aaa9a21398046b383d9f99ea1b3d0d4ad08ae","tid":1269523,"uid":85774,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:38:23.000Z","msg":"俾左幾多錢大會？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:50:29.000Z","msg":"姓燒嘅比唔比得起呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T18:27:41.000Z","msg":"知